value.value: A class II olfactory receptor that is a translation product of the human OR4F3, OR4F16, or OR4F29 genes, 1:1 orthologs thereof, or a semi-ortholog thereof.

definition.value: Category=gene. Note: The human OR4F3, OR4F16, and OR4F29 genes encode identical proteins.
